<div style="width:400px;text-align:right;float:right;margin: 10px 0 0 0">
&#8212;<span class="small">Apollodorus</span>, <i>The Library,</i> <a href="https://tinyurl.com/ya9vr7sr" target="_blank">1.6</a>
